http://www.thehindu.com/news/national/tamil-nadu/Noon-meal-organisers-cooks-to-be-recruited/article14024202.ece

As many as 484 organisers and 463 cooks are to be recruited for school noon meal programme in Tiruvannamalai district.According to a release from district collector A. Gnanasekaran, communal roaster, government norms and court directions would be adhered in the direct recruitment.On or before Feb. 5Interested women candidates whose age is between 21 and 40 may submit their applications with concerned blocks/ municipal offices on or before February 5.For the candidates belonging to Scheduled Tribe communities even those completed 18 years of age are eligible to be recruited.Educational qualification: for the post of noon meal organizer people who passed SSLC shall apply. For ST candidates, a pass/fail in class VIII is enough.For the post of cooks fifth pass is enough and for ST candidates just literacy is enough.